actions.text: Referred to House Committee on House Administration.

official_title: A resolution providing for printing additional copies of the Committee print entitled "7th Edition of the Immigration and Nationality Act with Amendments and Notes on Related Laws".

summary.text: Authorizes the printing of 12,000 additional copies of a committee print entitled "7th Edition of the Immigration and Nationality Act with Amendments and Notes on Related Laws". Specifies that 9,000 copies are for the use of the House of Representatives Committee on the Judiciary and 3,000 copies for the Senate Committee on the Judiciary.
